summary:
Over seventeen years of experience as an independent (free lance) tour guide in Egypt. Now living in the Netherlands I focus on giving language classes (Arabic), lectures (any topic related to Egypt, between everyday life and Egyptology), workshops (whether it's about Egyptian cooking or calligraphy) and special travel arrangements.

Specialties: Egyptology, Arabic language, Arabic art & culture, Egyptian music and movies, bellydance
